
======================================================================
PERSIST-002 Systemd timer creation [CRITICAL]
======================================================================

Category:
  Persistence  (detector: rules)

Description:
  Creating systemd timers enables periodic malware execution. Used
  in 2018 xeactor attack.

Recommendation:
  Timers should be user-controlled; review carefully

CWE: CWE-506

Real-World Context:
  Systemd persistence was used in both the 2018 xeactor attack
  (timers running every 360 seconds) and the July 2025 CHAOS RAT
  attack (services running at boot as default.target dependency).

======================================================================
